<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap');
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #1a202c;
            background-color: #f7fafc;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }
        
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        
        .header {
            padding: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 32px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -0.025em;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 35px 0;
        }
        
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4f46e5 0%, #6366f1 100%);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            letter-spacing: 0.025em;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.15);
        }
        
        .url-container {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .url-text {
            word-break: break-all;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #4f46e5;
            font-family: monospace;
        }
        
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .signature {
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .signature-text {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d3748;
        }
        
        .company-name {
            color: #4f46e5;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px 40px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #718096;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #718096;
            font-size: 13px;
        }
        
        .social-links {
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .social-icon {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            line-height: 32px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 50%;
            margin: 0 5px;
            color: #4a5568;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .expiry-notice {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #e53e3e;
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }
        
        .info-box {
            background-color: #ebf8ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #4299e1;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .button {
                padding: 12px 24px;
                font-size: 15px;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Rumor</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="greeting">Hello <%= name %>,</h1>
            
            <p>Thank you for joining Rumor! We're excited to have you as part of our community. To get started, please verify your email address by clicking the button below:</p>
            
            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="<%= url %>" class="button">Verify My Email</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>If the button above doesn't work, you can copy and paste the following URL into your web browser:</p>
            
            <div class="url-container">
                <span class="url-text"><%= url %></span>
            </div>
            
            <p class="expiry-notice">⏱️ This verification link will expire in 24 hours.</p>
            
            <div class="info-box">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">If you didn't sign up for a Rumor account, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="signature">
                <p class="signature-text">Welcome aboard,<br>The <span class="company-name">Rumor</span> Team</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2025 Rumor Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
            <!-- <p>123 App Street, San Francisco, CA 94107</p> -->
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">f</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">t</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">in</a>
                <a href="#" class="social-icon">ig</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>